{"tid":2310640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「我覺得會記得，所以唔使記錄」，辯方質疑「咁成份口供都唔使寫啦？」","createTime":"2020-12-03T11:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T11:59:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"464af5b1bcc1fb320879ecc3fc5e6f978a9ea510","tid":2310640,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\">「我覺得會記得，所以唔使記錄」，辯方質疑「咁成份口供都唔使寫啦？」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201203/KABN4VPPMZCCFDVE5CFF7GECWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201203%2FKABN4VPPMZCCFDVE5CFF7GECWE%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=248b402b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201203%2FKABN4VPPMZCCFDVE5CFF7GECWE%2F&h=0c7a8cde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201203/KABN4VPPMZCCFDVE5CFF7GECWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n頂證藏噴漆 自相矛盾隔半年「加料」<br />\n女警口供災難 錢詩文脫罪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前學民思潮成員錢詩文。。。。。。。。。。。。。點，裁定錢罪脫兼得訟費。<br />\n<br />\n今。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n女警員17517史穎珊。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/L-Liy2U4hekUFEBL4pleO4GDL0c=/720x1046/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MTRZVTLBUNFGVMI3ZRHTXFF35I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FL-Liy2U4hekUFEBL4pleO4GDL0c%3D%2F720x1046%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMTRZVTLBUNFGVMI3ZRHTXFF35I.jpg&h=5eb07eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■錢詩文昨出庭應訊，獲判罪名不成立兼得訟費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新聞片證說法構成嚴重疑點<br />\n<br />\n辯方大律師郭憬憲盤問下，史透露自己毅進課程畢業，懂聽及書寫中文。她的警察記事冊顯示，被告當時身穿灰色外套，辯方問她庭上說黑色風褸是否記錯，史承認，但否認辯方指她「直覺地覺得拉親嘅都係黑衣人」。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指，史在記事簿及最初一份口供從沒提及被捕人「逃跑」，卻於7月提交補充口供指被告曾逃走。史一度解釋對逃跑一事印象深刻，<span class=\"orange\">「我覺得會記得，所以唔使記錄」，辯方質疑「咁成份口供都唔使寫啦？」</span>史指最初口供資料出錯，才補錄新口供。辯方認為，實情是調查人員不滿史口供「唔夠料」指控被告，才要求添加逃跑情節。史否認。<br />\n<br />\n處理本案證物的偵緝警員16058區浩賢在書面口供提及，曾尋找女警查詢案件細節。辯方昨質疑他其實是要求女警在新口供添加被告逃跑情節，區否認。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官林子勤裁決指，女警原稱看見十多人聚集才下車追截，追問下變成被告衝向警車，才引發她下車追捕。事發當日的書面紀錄顯示被告靠近警車，但女警在半年後的新口供則指被告逃跑，出現不同版本，惟女警卻未能提供合理解釋，更指部份細節因印象深刻而毋須記下，難令人信服。<br />\n<br />\n林官指涉案背囊明顯是黑色，惟女警記錄背囊情況時，對顏色等細節的描述統統欠奉。有線電視直播畫面顯示，被告被捕後，女警或被告手上均沒拿着背囊，女警在庭上只稱背囊當時由她保管，但無法記起細節。林官形容新聞片段對女警說法構成嚴重疑點，控方無法證明背囊由被告管有，裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC2889/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bIBjFH8HLwP22YkwjcYsil1pC2w=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HCFDCPBXLBBO3LGCPJNZ7CPASI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbIBjFH8HLwP22YkwjcYsil1pC2w%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHCFDCPBXLBBO3LGCPJNZ7CPASI.jpg&h=8aad2aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■女警史穎珊證供被辯方質疑「大話冚大話」。"},{"pid":"c29f67e31c6dc60e5654eb4c9c824be478228831","tid":2310640,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"生豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588fcb5fb123934c3d12903ed527bfcf59c865b4","tid":2310640,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"成班狗造證據唔使本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f68fe2073569ac2f4f5bc35be58ffb463901b6b","tid":2310640,"uid":51024,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死tb核撚突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}